普照着终将消逝的黑夜。\n\n三联增订版的《人类的群星闪耀时》，将是国内迄今为止的最新版本，即将历史时刻特写从原来的12个增加到14个，所涉及的历史人物分别是西塞罗和“一战”时美国总统伍德罗•威尔逊。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T15:58:28.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#586888","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/3212f/_6be6300966.jpg","srcSet":"/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/5c809/_6be6300966.jpg 25w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/5c9f3/_6be6300966.jpg 50w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/3212f/_6be6300966.jpg 100w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/291ee/_6be6300966.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/7f5c9/_6be6300966.webp 25w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/de8f1/_6be6300966.webp 50w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/fd5fd/_6be6300966.webp 100w,\n/static/636506d9c0adbdb1480f5da1785c729e/436db/_6be6300966.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"a-brief-history-of-humankind","title":"人类简史","author":"[以色列] 尤瓦尔·赫拉利","description":"尤瓦尔·赫拉利，1976年生，牛津大学历史学博士，现为耶路撒冷希伯来大学的历史系教授，青年怪才，全球瞩目的新锐历史学家，擅长世界历史和宏观历史进程研究，在学术领域和大众出版领域都有很大的兴趣。《人类简史》一书让他一举成名，成为以色列超级畅销书，目前这本书已授20多个国家版权，在历史学之外，人类学、生态学、基因学等领域的知识信手拈来。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-03T08:13:41.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#d8d8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c809/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 25w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c9f3/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 50w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 100w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/291ee/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/